question_id: Pada tahun 2005, bulan apa yang mencatat total pembayaran terbesar? Sertakan nomor bulan (1–12) dan total pembayarannya.
sql_query:
SELECT
    substring(month(r.rental_date) FROM 1 LENGTH 2) AS bulan,
    SUM(p.amount) AS total_pembayaran
FROM
    rental r
JOIN
    payment p ON r.rental_id = p.rental_id
WHERE
    YEAR(r.rental_date) = 2005
GROUP BY
    bulan
ORDER BY
    total_pembayaran DESC
LIMIT 1
raw_response:
